{
  "page": "Folly",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>folly</b> is an event held in the <a href=\"/index.php/Fighting_pits\" title=\"Fighting pits\">fighting pits</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> where beasts are pitted against <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">slaves</a> who have no means of actually fighting to save their lives, such as small children, dwarfs, cripples or crones. The <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari\" title=\"Ghiscari\">Ghiscari</a> consider these events humorous.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Folly&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Folly&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>, when <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> is inspecting the <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> soldiers that she is considering purchasing, <a href=\"/index.php/Kraznys_mo_Nakloz\" title=\"Kraznys mo Nakloz\">Kraznys mo Nakloz</a> asks her if she wishes to view their fighting pits. Kraznys tells her that <a href=\"/index.php/Douquor%27s_Pit\" title=\"Douquor&#39;s Pit\">Douquor's Pit</a> has a \"fine folly\" scheduled for the evening – a <a href=\"/index.php/Bear\" title=\"Bear\">bear</a> and three small boys. One boy is to be rolled in honey, one in blood and one in rotting fish. Dany can wager on which the bear will eat first. Dany declines the invitation.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Folly&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> sought to end follies as part of her reforms to the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, but her consort <a href=\"/index.php/Hizdahr_zo_Loraq\" title=\"Hizdahr zo Loraq\">Hizdahr zo Loraq</a> convinced her that these are a source of income for dwarfs, cripples and crones - with Daenerys believing that the follies involve participants fighting each other instead of beasts. During the reopening of <a href=\"/index.php/Daznak%27s_Pit\" title=\"Daznak&#39;s Pit\">Daznak's Pit</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a>, slaves of <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Yunkish\">Yunkish</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Wise_Masters\" title=\"Wise Masters\">Wise Master</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Yezzan_zo_Qaggaz\" title=\"Yezzan zo Qaggaz\">Yezzan zo Qaggaz</a> perform their mock joust for Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>. Unbeknowst to them, <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lions</a> are about to be set loose on them but Daenerys halts it after finding out.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Folly&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 23\">Chapter 23</a>, Daenerys II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_52\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 52\">Chapter 52</a>, Daenerys IX.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404194455\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 210/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8586/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 753/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 44/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 987/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    7.357      1 -total\n 76.72%    5.644      2 Template:Ref\n 46.80%    3.443      2 Template:Ref/core\n 21.45%    1.578      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:23776-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404194455 and revision id 322584\n -->\n",
